            Aegis Lux motto!&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class="NewsUser">Errol 
            - 27-09-2000 at 07:27:46</span> 
            <br>
		  <span class="NewsTitleDescription">Aegis Lux's new motto has been found!</span>
		  </td>
          <td width="16" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">&nbsp;</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
        <tr bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
          <td width="32" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">&nbsp;</td>
          <td class="NewsText" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
            <br>
			What should our motto be?<br><br>The boards are filled with suggestions and the Council had it narrowed down to 5 choices.<br><br>We actually wanted to post a poll where people could vote, but seeing as the poles are accessible for non-members too, we chose to simply gather the votes from the boards.<br><br>Many voted in favor of another latin addition, but in the end most people agreed on the most simple approach.<br><br>The new motto for Aegis Lux is:<br><br><b>Aegis Lux!</b><br><br>It is what defines us. We are The Shield of Light.<br><br>So be it.
          </td>
          <td width="16" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">&nbsp;</td>
        </tr>
