          <td class="NewsEnd" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><br>
		  Feel free to discuss my decision on the Private Messageboard. A new poll is also up to measure whether I am way off or not on this ;-)
		  </td>
          <td width="16" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">&nbsp;</td>
