			The Dalnirs Crypt event.<br><br>A harsh lesson in what happens when we go deep into enemy territory, without a concise plan or preparation.<br><br><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td><div align="center"><img src="/Images/nibbler.jpg" width="400" height="300"></div></td></tr></table><br><b><i>Arhh..Bite me!!</i></b><br><br>We have learned from this experience. And are wiser now. As we should be. Stronger in our determination. We were being tested, brothers and sisters. And we passed.<br><br>- Errol
