            Rescue me!&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class="NewsUser">Errol 
            - 05-09-2000 at 13:27:44</span> 
            <br>
		  <span class="NewsTitleDescription">Aegis Lux rescued two of our brothers deep inside Dalnirs...</span>
		  </td>
          <td width="16" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">&nbsp;</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
        <tr bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
          <td width="32" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">&nbsp;</td>
          <td class="NewsText" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
            <br>
			After falling victim to the sinister inhabitants of Dalnirs Crypt in Kunark two days ago, Arthun and Avrohom needed help.They both died deep within the Crypt and Aegis Lux mounted a rescue operation to help them regain their alter ego's.<br><br>With the aid of Shadowcloak the Omnipotent and her awe-inspiring pet, a group of persistent brothers and sisters delved deeply into Dalnirs and rescued our two stranded friends.<br><br>Thanks goes out to Wizbane, Eloron, Pulga, Shadowcloak, Zimpzon and ofcourse Rapsodi, who pulled Avi's corpse.<br><br>Also, to Fawna who guided us through the wilderness and Armedia, who escorted us most of the way.<br><br>Hope I didn't forget anyone???<br><br>Friends, you all did well, showing true Aegisian spirit.<br><br>Hail Aegis Lux!<br><br>- Errol
          </td>
          <td width="16" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">&nbsp;</td>
        </tr>
