            <br>
			Try checking out the <b>Our Legacy</b> section. Here you will find a complete account of the Entire Norrathian history (or at least what we have been able to dig up so far).<br><br>Remember that the Council haven't written this, but merely collected the scraps. The authors are still unknown.<br><br>But go check it out! Learn about Kedge Keep, the Dragons, Innoruuk and the Battle of Kithicor. Don't cheat yourself of this amazing background.<br><br>- Errol
